# BoxSync Admin

Multi-tenant staff dashboard for CrossFit boxes worldwide. Stack: Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, TypeScript, Supabase, Tailwind 4.

## Structure

- `lib/services/` — Supabase queries (athleteService, classService, financialService, …)
- `lib/types/gym.ts` — domain types (Profile, Booking, ExpenseRecord, …)
- `app/dashboard/<feature>/` — pages, optional `hooks/`, `actions.ts`
- `app/api/admin/` — staff API; use `requireStaffApi()` first

## Code style

- Functional components, custom hooks for page data
- Services export plain objects with async methods — no classes
- Throw on Supabase errors in services; map to safe user messages in UI/auth helpers
- Use `@/` path alias for imports
- Brand color: `pits-red` (Tailwind). Sidebar: dark gray-900, main: gray-50

## Scope

- Minimal diffs only — no drive-by refactors or unrelated files
- Reuse existing modals, Toast, ConfirmDialog, Tooltip
- No new dependencies without explicit request
- No markdown/docs files unless requested

## Multi-tenant (all new work)

Add `box_id` to tenant data. Every query/mutation must scope by active box. See `AGENTS.md` for full tenancy plan.
